{"metadata": {"description": "Spark an interest in the skilled trades! This program introduces what a trade is and gets you involved in hands-on activities.", "robots": "index, follow", "og:site_name": "SkilledTradesBC", "og:type": "landing-page", "og:url": "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/youth-discover-trades-program", "og:title": "Youth Discover the Trades Program | SkilledTradesBC", "og:description": "Spark an interest in the skilled trades! This program introduces what a trade is and gets you involved in hands-on activities.", "twitter:card": "summary_large_image", "twitter:description": "Spark an interest in the skilled trades! This program introduces what a trade is and gets you involved in hands-on activities.", "twitter:site": "@SkilledTradesBC", "Generator": "Drupal 11 (https://www.drupal.org)", "MobileOptimized": "width", "HandheldFriendly": "true", "viewport": "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", "title": "Youth Discover the Trades Program | SkilledTradesBC"}, "markdown": "Skip to main content \n\n###### Menu\n\n____ Show/hide collapsed content\n\nYouth Discover the Trades Programs will get you talking about trades. The programs vary from one-day events with local tradespeople to regular classroom activities that incorporate trades thinking and skill building. Students learn about what a trade is and why trades are awesome! \n\nYour project must offer hands-on trade experiences for students in grades 5 through 10. It should include additional classroom learning both before and after the event. \n\n**Forms for Educators:**\n\n  1. [Youth Discover the Trades Application](/media/1170/download)\n\n  2. [Youth Discover the Trades Lesson Plan](/media/1792/download)\n\n  3. [Youth Discover the Trades Completion Report](/media/1790/download)\n\n  4. [Media Consent Form](https://analytics.clickdimensions.com/cn/adufq/consent-form)\n\n  5. [Youth Discover the Trades Activity Ideas and Tips Sheet](/media/1793/download)\n\n\n\n\nResources for Educators \n\nGet classroom resources, youth program guides, workbooks, and more. \n\n[ Get Resources](/resources-for-educators)\n\nYouth Explore\n\nthe Trades\n\nTry out different trades! The Youth Explore programs give you the chance to build skills and get hands-on experience.\n\n[ Learn More](/youth-explore-the-trades-program)\n\nYouth Train\n\nin Trades\n\nGet a head-start in trades training! This program is perfect for those looking to build their skills and experience in a specific trade while attending high school.\n\n[ Learn More](/youth-train-in-trades-program)\n", "links": ["https://portal.skilledtradesbc.ca/SignIn/", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-skilledtradesbc", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-the-trades", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-trades-about-skilledtradesbc-corporate-reports/public-interest-disclosure-act", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-trades-about-skilledtradesbc/corporate-reports", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-trades-indigenous-peoples-trades/employment-training-support", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-trades-indigenous-peoples-trades/indigenous-youth", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/about-trades/skilledtradesbc-news-feed", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/accessibility-plan", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/annual-reports", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/apprentice-mobility", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/are-you-impacted", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/become-an-apprentice", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/canada-apprentice-loans", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/canadian-and-military-certificate-holders", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/careers-at-skilledtradesbc", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/challenge-certification-exam", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/challenge-level-exam", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/challenge-skilled-trade", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/connect-with-a-school", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/contact-us", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/disclaimer", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/employment-insurance", "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/equity